{"analytics_identifier":"PC1434","base_path":"/government/organisations/dft-operator-limited","content_id":"d96162f6-2fe4-40cd-8eac-0a6ac08254fd","description":"DfT Operator Limited (DFTO) is the government’s public sector rail owning group. DFTO’s purpose is to bring all currently privately-owned train operators into public ownership in advance of the creation of Great British Railways in 2027. DFTO is a public corporation of the Department for Transport .","details":{"acronym":"DFTO","alternative_format_contact_email":"enquires@dftoperator.co.uk","body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>DfT Operator Limited (DFTO) is the government’s public sector rail owning group. DFTO’s purpose is to bring all currently privately-owned train operators into public ownership in advance of the creation of Great British Railways in 2027.</p>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"DfT Operator Limited\">DFTO</abbr> is a public corporation of the <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/department-for-transport\">Department for Transport</a>.</p>\n</div>","brand":"department-for-transport","default_news_image":{"high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/675041b4d12a2dad3bc97a6e/s960_swr-winnersh-960.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/675041b42956d2d4b1632a58/s300_swr-winnersh-960.jpg"},"foi_exempt":false,"logo":{"crest":"custom","formatted_title":"DfT Operator Limited","image":{"alt_text":"DfT Operator Limited","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/678dfa9193d4eae3088bd3d5/dfto-logo.jpg"}},"ordered_corporate_information_pages":[{"href":"/government/organisations/dft-operator-limited/about/complaints-procedure","title":"Complaints procedure"},{"href":"https://dfto.recruitgenie.co.uk/jobs.aspx","title":"Jobs"}],"ordered_featured_documents":[{"document_type":"Press release","href":"/government/news/dfto-takes-next-steps-towards-great-british-railways","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69c12dfd7e02b81c0d1c7649/s712_laura-shoaf.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69c12dfd7e02b81c0d1c7647/s465_laura-shoaf.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69c12dfdb920af63be1c765e/laura-shoaf.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2026-03-20T12:00:00.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Laura Shoaf and Tony Poulter join the Department for Transport Operator (DFTO) board, helping to set up Great British Railways (GBR).</p>\n</div>","title":"DFTO takes next steps towards Great British Railways"},{"document_type":"News story","href":"/government/news/west-midlands-trains-services-transferred","image":{"alt_text":"West Midlands Railway","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/698075d4f0e5cf1ed2612db6/s712_west-midlands-railway-960.png","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/698075d43915f712365800bf/s465_west-midlands-railway-960.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/698075d4ec71a16669612db8/west-midlands-railway-960.png"},"public_updated_at":"2026-02-01T02:00:04.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>West Midlands Trains services are now managed by DfT Operator Ltd (DFTO).</p>\n</div>","title":"West Midlands Trains services transferred"},{"document_type":"Press release","href":"/government/news/london-northwestern-railway-and-west-midlands-railway-services-return-to-public-ownership","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/697c68afb28b2cc262572f57/s712_wmt-960.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/697c68af2ff8d10a830d5d8d/s465_wmt-960.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/697c68af87922ed83d0d5d81/wmt-960.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2026-01-30T00:01:00.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>From 1 February 2026, passengers who travel with London Northwestern Railway and West Midlands Railway will benefit from reliable and better-connected services.</p>\n</div>","title":"London Northwestern Railway and West Midlands Railway services return to public ownership"},{"document_type":"Press release","href":"/government/news/new-chairs-of-network-rail-and-dfto-named","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/697c695c2ff8d10a830d5d8e/s712_andrew-haines-960.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/697c695cb28b2cc262572f59/s465_andrew-haines-960.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/697c695cb28b2cc262572f5a/andrew-haines-960.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2026-01-12T14:00:00.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Richard George and Sir Andrew Haines bring extensive experience to help improve passenger experience and operational performance we will see under Great British Railways.</p>\n</div>","title":"New chairs of Network Rail and DFTO named"},{"document_type":"Press release","href":"/government/news/alex-hynes-named-as-new-ceo-of-dft-operator","image":{"alt_text":"Alex Hynes.","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/692859face50d215cae96147/s712_alex-hynes-portrait-960.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/692859fa9c1eda2cdf0341f0/s465_alex-hynes-portrait-960.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/692859f99c1eda2cdf0341ef/alex-hynes-portrait-960.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2025-11-27T00:00:00.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Alex Hynes appointed CEO of DFTO to lead rail reform, as more operators move into public ownership ahead of Great British Railways launch.</p>\n</div>","title":"Alex Hynes named as new CEO of DfT Operator"},{"document_type":"News story","href":"/government/news/greater-anglia-services-transferred-to-public-ownership","image":{"alt_text":"Greater Anglia","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/68ecb560ba06a9bb2a8aeac7/s712_greater-anglia-3.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/68ecb5604d840b4b808aeacb/s465_greater-anglia-3.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/68ecb560ba06a9bb2a8aeac5/greater-anglia-3.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2025-10-12T02:00:00.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Greater Anglia services are now managed by DfT Operator Ltd (DFTO).</p>\n</div>","title":"Greater Anglia services transferred to public ownership"}],"ordered_featured_links":[],"ordered_promotional_features":[],"organisation_featuring_priority":"news","organisation_govuk_status":{"status":"live","updated_at":null,"url":null},"organisation_political":false,"organisation_type":"public_corporation","secondary_corporate_information_pages":"Read about the types of information we routinely publish in our <a class=\"govuk-link brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/dft-operator-limited/about/publication-scheme\">Publication scheme</a>. Our <a class=\"govuk-link brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/dft-operator-limited/about/personal-information-charter\">Personal information charter</a> explains how we treat your personal information.","social_media_links":[]},"document_type":"organisation","first_published_at":"2024-12-04T09:02:24+00:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"analytics_identifier":"PC1434","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/dft-operator-limited","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/dft-operator-limited","base_path":"/government/organisations/dft-operator-limited","content_id":"d96162f6-2fe4-40cd-8eac-0a6ac08254fd","document_type":"organisation","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2026-03-20T12:15:10Z","schema_name":"organisation","title":"DfT Operator Limited","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/dft-operator-limited","withdrawn":false}],"ordered_board_members":[{"api_path":"/api/content/governme